3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for depth estimation. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with the problem of depth estimation, which is important in computer graphics. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as depth estimation is an important problem in robotics for tasks such as object recognition and manipulation.
